I'm not sure if I'm doing the vertex setup correctly.

Replacing the whole terrain system into a new one. The full code I'm testing is on Urho. Basically,
I want to project a cube to a sphere, Terrain=WorldTerrain, TerrainFace, then TerrainPatches(Working similiar in how the patch works without additional nodes)

Any help or idea would be helpful.

