Currently I learn box2D documentation http://box2d.org/manual.pdf and SDK and I think Urho uses b2world->Step() incorrect.

In fuction void Step(float32 timeStep, int32 velocityIterations, int32 positionIterations)
timeStep is frequency actually.

In standart examples box2d do not use time intervals: timeStep = 1 / HZ always. (1 / 60.0f for example)

